[2] Liberia: US journalist with Ebola being evacuated
Date: Fri 3 Oct 2014
Source: Wall Street Journal [edited]
http://online.wsj.com/articles/u-s-journalist-tests-positive-for-ebola-1412340037


AM, an American freelance journalist diagnosed with Ebola, and the NBC News team he worked with here will be flown to the USA, yet another demonstration of the international repercussions of the epidemic sweeping West Africa. AM is scheduled to be picked up Sunday night [5 Oct 2014] in Liberia and will be transported to the Nebraska Medical Center in Omaha, his father said Friday [3 Oct 2014].

